# Task 20 – Document Setup Manual

## Project

Smart Library Request Workflow in ServiceNow

## Description

This document provides a step-by-step guide for recreating the Smart Library Request Workflow application in a new ServiceNow Personal Developer Instance (PDI).

## Setup Steps

1. Create Roles
2. Create Custom Tables
3. Configure Table Fields
4. Configure Reference Qualifier
5. Create Flow Designer Workflow
6. Configure UI Policy
7. Configure Access Control Lists (ACLs)
8. Create Reports
9. Insert Test Data
10. Validate the Complete Workflow

## Validation

- Borrow Request Approval Flow
- Book Status Updates
- Return Process
- ACL Verification
- UI Policy Validation
- Report Generation

## Technologies Used

- ServiceNow
- Flow Designer
- UI Policies
- Access Control Lists (ACLs)
- Reports
- Reference Qualifiers

## Status

Completed
